# Stray IntelliJ Java project accidentally created inside the repo (not part of the app).
# Anchored to repo root with a leading slash: an unanchored "ApplyMate/" also
# matches android/.../com/example/applymate/ on case-insensitive filesystems
# (Windows/macOS), which silently ignored MainActivity.kt and broke the build.
/ApplyMate/

